{"tid":635281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：中國一直有港主權　「收回」不正確  聯合聲明第一條: 收回香港是全中國人民的共同願望，中共決定對香港恢復行使主權","createTime":"2018-04-20T04:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T08:45:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"88577aad09318dc09d695c2a22fd272e37310cb9","tid":635281,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:09:33.000Z","msg":"有線新聞早前教育局今年審核歷史課本時，要求出版局修改「香港位於中國南方」、「中國收回香港」等一直沿用的字眼。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">教育局局長楊潤雄在立法會財務委員會特別會議上回應議員提問時指，中國一直擁有香港主權，故「收回」之說並不正確。</span></strong>郭家麟反譏當局，不如使用中共黨史或內地教科書，楊潤雄回應時指稱可考慮使用國家的教科書，他又指不反對香港教科書出版社用內地教科書作參考。<br />\n<br />\n議員郭家麒質問楊潤雄這一年來發生過甚麼事，為何當局一直容許使用有關字句，但今年卻需要修改。楊潤雄指，審核教科書時必須要顧及前文後理。楊潤雄舉例指，「香港位於中國的南方」在語文上不清晰，可以代表香港在中國境內或境外的南方，故有需要修改。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對於「中國收回香港」一說，楊潤雄指，歷史上中國一直具有香港的主權，所以不涉及任何收回，或由英國交回香港主權的說法。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n郭家麟譏用內地教科書   楊潤雄：會考慮下<br />\n<br />\n郭家麟在提問時，以反詰口脗說，既然要書商猜度政治正確的思想，「不如將中共黨史或內地教科書俾我哋」。楊潤雄回應時指：「郭家麒議員提議話將國家的教科書擺嚟香港，如果係郭家麒提議，我會考慮下。」楊潤雄又指，不反對香港教科書出版社用內地教科書作參考，「因為佢哋可以攞各類的書嚟參考」。<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞早前取得一份教育局的課本評審報告，發現今年中史課本內的不少字眼都被要求修改，包括「香港主權移交中國內地」、「中共一黨專政」等以往一直沿用的說法。浸會大學新聞系高級講師呂秉權質疑，有關做法是否出於政治需要，又形容「黑手」正伸向和滲透香港歷史教科書。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%B2%E6%9B%B8%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A-%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E-%E4%B9%8B%E8%AA%AA%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%8D%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9-%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258F%25B2%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25AD%2597%25E7%259C%25BC-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%259B%259E-%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25A2%25BA-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2596%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%2599%25B0%2F&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=3e16e974\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258F%25B2%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25AD%2597%25E7%259C%25BC-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%259B%259E-%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25A2%25BA-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2596%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%2599%25B0%2F&h=43b74a17\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%B2%E6%9B%B8%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A-%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E-%E4%B9%8B%E8%AA%AA%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%8D%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9-%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0/</a>"},{"pid":"7bb2796c041ab134d263242e55941df4f3a5a28c","tid":635281,"uid":48083,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國政府和大不列顛及北愛爾蘭聯合王國政府滿意地回顧了近年來兩國政府和兩國人民之間的友好關係，一致認為通過協商妥善地解決歷史上遺留下來的香港問題，有助於維持香港的繁榮與穩定，並有助於兩國關係在新的基礎上進一步鞏固和發展，為此，經過兩國政府代表團的會談，同意聲明如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一、中華人民共和國政府聲明：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收回</span>香港地區（包括香港島、九龍和&ldquo;新界&rdquo;，以下稱香港）是全中國人民的共同願望，中華人民共和國政府決定於１９９７年７月１日對香港<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>恢復</ins>行使主權</span>。</strong></span><br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmab.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fissues%2Fjd2.htm&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=89177bbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n冇失去過權又洗咩恢復??<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結論:<br />\n同中国人講信用講合約精神<br />\n係哂鳩氣</span></span></strong></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"2b29635da1477ac1727d4cca7b732ab0e5b5854d","tid":635281,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> chi na人"},{"pid":"362274b2fadc3db65c7e388e6af982c862dbb05e","tid":635281,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"美國action<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fc4c8912c65ddbe670ed4c52450188a573c763","tid":635281,"uid":63909,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:15:52.000Z","msg":"呢條友去管教育<br />\n屌你香港邊有救<br />\n仆你個街完全同立場都無撚關係<br />\n根本係大話"},{"pid":"2aa7af8f7eb3ac94feed2f967f54a8dd3735e26c","tid":635281,"uid":72186,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"以前英屬香港 而家中屬香港<br />\n未來 香港"},{"pid":"cb5062db14e06d3b56dba6e25c2f71d867f1d885","tid":635281,"uid":166675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:29:38.000Z","msg":"港豬要由小陪養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ead95f3e1d870f2d33ce611f768e910a03de75","tid":635281,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7bb2796c041ab134d263242e55941df4f3a5a28c","tid":635281,"uid":48083,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國政府和大不列顛及北愛爾蘭聯合王國政府滿意地回顧了近年來兩國政府和兩國人民之間的友好關係，一致認為通過協商妥善地解決歷史上遺留下來的香港問題，有助於維持香港的繁榮與穩定，並有助於兩國關係在新的基礎上進一步鞏固和發展，為此，經過兩國政府代表團的會談，同意聲明如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一、中華人民共和國政府聲明：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收回</span>香港地區（包括香港島、九龍和&ldquo;新界&rdquo;，以下稱香港）是全中國人民的共同願望，中華人民共和國政府決定於１９９７年７月１日對香港<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>恢復</ins>行使主權</span>。</strong></span><br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmab.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fissues%2Fjd2.htm&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=89177bbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n冇失去過權又洗咩恢復??<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結論:<br />\n同中国人講信用講合約精神<br />\n係哂鳩氣</span></span></strong></strong></span></div>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"佢會話中國一直有香港主權，但在1997年前無行使"},{"pid":"1ccfb290cc14ac9712e50bf38b192f896b66ffe3","tid":635281,"uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:34:47.000Z","msg":"你唔係唔知九龍半島同香港島係永久割讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b58dbb1e7e3541df0eab35dfbcb686b0d4c1949","tid":635281,"uid":5502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:38:40.000Z","msg":"點解香港班歷史學者今次唔聯署抗議?<br />\n前年講支那發晒聲明屌人"},{"pid":"91d3c7706db2f75af8d17df9adfd9e776f4d3207","tid":635281,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b58dbb1e7e3541df0eab35dfbcb686b0d4c1949","tid":635281,"uid":5502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:38:40.000Z","msg":"點解香港班歷史學者今次唔聯署抗議?<br />\n前年講支那發晒聲明屌人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"全部都係奴才"},{"pid":"57a3943c77dd41519665816feb5b1442801ea386","tid":635281,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0