的共同願望，中華人民共和國政府決定於１９９７年７月１日對香港<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>恢復</ins>行使主權</span>。</strong></span><br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmab.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fissues%2Fjd2.htm&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=89177bbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n冇失去過權又洗咩恢復??<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結論:<br />\n同中国人講信用講合約精神<br />\n係哂鳩氣</span></span></strong></strong></span></div>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"佢會話中國一直有香港主權，但在1997年前無行使"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:28:39.000Z","msg":"個合約用英文為主 <br />\n<br />\n鬼婆都知你實打飛機亂改 所以理得你中文想寫咩"},{"pid":"20026be00863ee2398fba4c2ae48301f83f9f9cf","tid":635281,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個合約用英文為主 <br />\n<br />\n鬼婆都知你實打飛機亂改 所以理得你中文想寫咩</blockquote><br />\n做狗官為個立場連基本常識都唔洗睇<br />\n<br />\n首先如果佢話嘅野係真，全港999年地契果堆地唔該廢晒佢收番佢先"},{"pid":"6afa149381b337d7b3b017524fbf35b5b9543c33","tid":635281,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"f72246bf77ec4a8d894af12b3d62f092669cc833","tid":635281,"uid":83097,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:45:40.000Z","msg":"遲早殺左楊潤雄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:58:07.000Z","msg":"安已不<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}